<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>zhì sǐ shùn fú xiàng gāo yáng 迦南648</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 zhì sǐ shùn fú xiàng gāo yáng, shì sǐ rú guī huí jiā xiāng.
 bù zài huí yì guò qù yǒu duō shǎo cāng sāng, bù zài tàn xún lái lái yǒu duō shǎo fēng làng.
 yīn zhǔ zài shēn páng suí shí jiā lì liàng. shòu kǔ shì zhǔ zhǐ yì, dōu jì zài tiān shàng.
 chuán fú yīn zài zhè kuài rè tǔ shàng. suī rán liú làng xīn què tián mì, yī lù bǎ gē chàng.</lyrics>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<hymn_number>648</hymn_number>
</song>